(36403, 0, 2, 'I can''t help but think that if it weren''t for the meddling of $N back on Kezan, we''d all be safe and sound in Azshara by now.', 14, 0, 100, 5, 0, 19590, 'Trade Prince Gallywix'),
(36403, 0, 3, 'Oh, I think we all know who''s really responsible for the mess we''re in! Don''t worry, I''m going to see to it that $N gets what $g he : she; deserves!', 14, 0, 100, 5, 0, 19587, 'Trade Prince Gallywix');
